# Claude Adapter

Read `AGENTS.md` first. That file is the shared repository contract for all
agents.

This file should stay thin and contain only Claude-specific additions:

- keep repository policy and workflow rules in `AGENTS.md`
- use Claude-specific hooks only when the repository has chosen to enable them
- do not duplicate general architecture workflow rules here unless Claude needs
  stricter wording for a known behavior difference

If this repository already has a `CLAUDE.md`, merge the agent-arch guidance into
that file instead of keeping two competing instruction sources.
